    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >天上飞的是鸟吗？还是飞机？都不是，那只是不受待见的英雄罢了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他们会帮忙拯救世界吗？那还真不一定，他们很可能还会给你添乱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超级大礼包中包含20种全新装备，其中6种是超能力装备，同时还有6个新本能以及2种全新的山羊。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >下面让我们热烈欢迎超级六羊组！谁会成为你心目中的英雄？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299590/extras/726c1d56c94180b93b57f933642260f2.avif?t=1734014574\" width=616 height=300 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 迪格雷博士：比你的前任还要让你感到心寒</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299590/extras/a490fc1e4ce14bad2a2e429d21a64af6.poster.avif?t=1734014574\" width=250 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299590/extras/a490fc1e4ce14bad2a2e429d21a64af6.webm?t=1734014574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299590/extras/a490fc1e4ce14bad2a2e429d21a64af6.mp4?t=1734014574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >克里姆森·克罗森：还记得你妈用人字拖揍你时的样子吗？她只会更狠</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299590/extras/31604a6d81ff4176341d9c801dde3e28.poster.avif?t=1734014574\" width=250 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299590/extras/31604a6d81ff4176341d9c801dde3e28.webm?t=1734014574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299590/extras/31604a6d81ff4176341d9c801dde3e28.mp4?t=1734014574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >超级山羊：比你们这些普通山羊更强壮、更聪明，反正就是比你们厉害</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299590/extras/67f44f0d15a89d8b6140b7a9c4c0ea53.poster.avif?t=1734014574\" width=250 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299590/extras/67f44f0d15a89d8b6140b7a9c4c0ea53.webm?t=1734014574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299590/extras/67f44f0d15a89d8b6140b7a9c4c0ea53.mp4?t=1734014574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >曼瑟诺斯：可以通过喷射臭气来传送。听起来就跟我那邋遢的男朋友一样<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299590/extras/0d29740329c9f14c25311f538ce43c72.poster.avif?t=1734014574\" width=250 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299590/extras/0d29740329c9f14c25311f538ce43c72.webm?t=1734014574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299590/extras/0d29740329c9f14c25311f538ce43c72.mp4?t=1734014574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不动如山女士：你可以把她当成巨型岩石版山羊</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299590/extras/c072fc25419eaaaccae77706a778b9cc.poster.avif?t=1734014574\" width=250 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299590/extras/c072fc25419eaaaccae77706a778b9cc.webm?t=1734014574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299590/extras/c072fc25419eaaaccae77706a778b9cc.mp4?t=1734014574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >树桩：你可能会好奇它在做什么，实际上它已经很努力想要动起来了</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299590/extras/62f8462e718f4e8b01564efcc170c712.poster.avif?t=1734014574\" width=250 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299590/extras/62f8462e718f4e8b01564efcc170c712.webm?t=1734014574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299590/extras/62f8462e718f4e8b01564efcc170c712.mp4?t=1734014574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >完整的超级大礼包内含：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-迪格雷博士的皮毛</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-迪格雷博士的冰角</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-迪格雷博士的冷冻装置</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-迪格雷博士的冷冻靴子</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-克里姆森·克罗森的皮毛</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-克里姆森·克罗森套装</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-克里姆森·克罗森头饰</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-克里姆森·克罗森的靴子</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-超级山羊套装</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-超级山羊头盔</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-超级山羊面具</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-超级山羊兜帽</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-超级山羊披风</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-超级山羊靴子</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-曼瑟诺斯的皮毛</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-曼瑟诺斯之气</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-曼瑟诺斯的靴子</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-不动如山女士</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-树桩</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-副腿</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299590/extras/cc15c0cddd693cca37224f064a21f1dc.poster.avif?t=1734014574\" width=250 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299590/extras/cc15c0cddd693cca37224f064a21f1dc.webm?t=1734014574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299590/extras/cc15c0cddd693cca37224f064a21f1dc.mp4?t=1734014574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
